data.description: Welcome to Patriots Village of Westpoint. This townhome is just couple months short of being 1 year old. The home has 2 bedrooms, 1 downstairs and one upstairs. Each with attached full bathroom. Great Room, Dining Area, Kitchen with granite countertops. Beautiful Luxury Vinyl Plank Flooring in foyer, Kitchen, bathrooms and laundry area. Nice back patio and easy access to Williamsburg and Richmond.
